Study

Common states: Pending, CrashLoopBackOff, ImagePullBackOff, ErrImagePull, OOMKilled, Evicted, Init:0/1.
Debug toolkit: describe, logs --previous, events, get pod -o yaml, kubectl debug, ephemeral containers.
Network debug: nslookup, wget, nc from a debug pod.
Hands-On

Deliberately break things and diagnose:
Wrong image tag → ImagePullBackOff.
Bad command → CrashLoopBackOff. Check kubectl logs --previous.
Memory hog with low limit → OOMKilled.
PVC not bound → pod Pending. Check kubectl describe pvc.
Taint without toleration → pod Pending. Check kubectl describe pod events.
